<html xmlns:i18n="http://namespaces.zope.org/i18n">
  <body>
    <p i18n:translate="">Hello,</p>
    <p i18n:translate="">
      We have received your request to subscribe to news notifications on the
      website of the Copernicus Land Monitoring Service. Please follow this
      <a i18n:translate="" i18n:name="url" href="${url}">link</a> to confirm
      your choice.
    </p>

    <p i18n:translate="">
      You can cancel your subscription anytime by clicking on this
      <a i18n:translate="" i18n:name="url" href="${unsubscribe_url}">link</a>.
    </p>

    <p i18n:translate="">
      If you have any questions please contact us at copernicus@eea.europa.eu.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="">
      Best regards, <br />Copernicus Land Monitoring Service
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
